      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Step into perfection with this stunning vehicle that looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! This car is in truly mint condition, meticulously maintained and preserved in pristine state inside and out. It's a rare find for a discerning buyer who wants a top-tier driving experience without a single blemish to worry about. Don't miss your chance to own this absolute gem!",
