    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior looks great with only minor stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with careful use, while the interior remains clean and comfortable with some light wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, the car is solid; the engine runs smoothly, the transmission shifts as it should, and all major electronics are fully functional. This is an excellent choice for someone looking for a reliable, attractive daily driver that has many miles of dependable service left to offer.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age. The engine starts consistently and the car is mechanically sound for regular use, but you may notice some minor fluid seepage and a suspension that feels less firm than it once was. Visually, the exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor dings, and some fading in the clear coat, while the interior shows significant wear on the driver\u2019s seat and some staining on the carpets. It is a functional option for someone looking for a dependable vehicle who isn't concerned with cosmetic perfection or may want to perform some light restorative work.",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
